widgets_values:
Image based prompt for Flux Dev with Upscaler

The workflow 
Upscaling is done using Ultimate SD Upscaler which is utilising Flux Dev model to upscale (not SD or SDXL). So it leverages the true power of this model and supports the use of a LoRA. You do need to get the select your choise of Upscaler model.



More workflows are shared at https://weirdwonderfulai.art - search "flux" to find it.

This allows for Image to Prompt using Florence 2 Model + Clip which interrogates the Image and creates the prompt using Natuarl Language.

You can combine with Manual Prompt as prefix if you enter something in there for the prompt to include. This could be a "Trigger" word of a lora for example. 

This kind of IPADAPTER until we have IPAdapter for Flux DEV.


TO ENABLE/DISABLE

Set the Use LLM for PROMPT switch.
TRUE means the Image is used and prompt is created by combining the image prompt and manual prompt

FALSE means it does not use the prompt generated from the Image but only your Manual Prompt.

widgets_values: The image shows a large robot standing on a snowy mountain landscape. The robot has a large round head with two large blue eyes and two antennae on top. It has two arms and two legs that are stretched out in front of it. The body of the robot is made up of multiple arms and legs, and it appears to be made of metal or plastic. The background shows a vast expanse of snow-covered mountains and a clear blue sky. In the foreground, there is a person walking towards the robot. The overall mood of the image is eerie and mysterious.There is a man that is standing in the dark with a cell phone
